Installation instructions for Linux operation system
====================================================
update cucc!!!!

   chc-0.2-1.i386.rpm
   chc-0.2-i586-1.txz
   chc-0.2.package
   chc-0.2-i586.tar.gz         binary package
   chc-0.2-i586.bin            installer programme
   chc_0.2-1_i386.deb          binary package

b. for Windows
   chc-0.2-win32.zip           binary package
   chc-0.2-win32.exe           installer application
   chc-0.2-win32.msi           binary package

c. source code
   chc-0.2.tar.gz              source package










1. Install
----------

a. Installation from binary '.tar.gz' package

    # cp chc-0.1-i586.tar.gz /opt
    # cd /opt
    # tar -xzf chc-0.1-i586.tar.gz
    # cd chc
    # ./create_links

                or

    # tar -xzf chc-0.1-i586.tar.gz
    # cd chc
    # ./install

b. Installation from '.bin' package

    # ./chc-0.1-i586.bin

c. Installation from source package
     
    # tar -xzf chc-0.1.tar.gz
    # ./configure
    # make
    # make install

2. Uninstall
------------

a. If you installed it from binary '.tar.gz' package

    # /opt/chc/remove_links
    # rm -r /opt/chc/

            or

    # /opt/chc/uninstall

b. If you installed it from '.bin' package

    # /opt/chc/uninstall

c. If you installed it from source package:

    # make uninstall

